description.en: The Solana HODL Whales are a collection of 3,000 unique whales that are fleeing Earth in the year 6969 trying to avoid extinction. They're on a search for their power source $KRILL that will be essential to sustaining their lives, their companions, and eventually their babies. Our model: breed, stake, earn.
